{"tid":2278510,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"內地真人版《棋魂》強加回歸情節捱轟 導演：香港回歸是中國人的集體回憶","createTime":"2020-11-09T08:13:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T02:47:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":106,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c926fce153bd9fa92a58315ad2e354ca20e0a4af","tid":2278510,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"日本知名動漫《棋靈王》早年風靡亞洲，近日更被中國製片公司翻拍成真人版網絡連續劇《棋魂》。除了角色名稱被大改外，更因強行加插「香港回歸」的情節而被輿論批評摧毀「經典」，網民紛呼崩潰。《棋魂》的導演劉暢日前接受內媒訪問時回應指，香港回歸是所有中國人的集體回憶，認為「香港回歸這件事本身給劇中人物的情緒底色會增加一些，看起來戲劇感也更強一些」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201109/2X3N3W7Y6VCV3O6SC7BFMX2X2Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201109%2F2X3N3W7Y6VCV3O6SC7BFMX2X2Q%2F&d=FEHxtXJUwAnPMx50BANU%2BfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=517c7772\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201109%2F2X3N3W7Y6VCV3O6SC7BFMX2X2Q%2F&h=b58ae6d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201109/2X3N3W7Y6VCV3O6SC7BFMX2X2Q/</a>"},{"pid":"a178ceff993dbc5434136b0c7885cc4c674a75d8","tid":2278510,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"ee6247926dbefbc2e470de48f88bf5050054b920","tid":2278510,"uid":25676,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:04:30.000Z","msg":"執柒咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f50340997258aa4730a1849d1ff6bceea78e5f","tid":2278510,"uid":470,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n最好加埋反日回憶 手撕皇軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7427e6cf96d521effccb95f503ff5868f4095928","tid":2278510,"uid":2142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T10:08:14.000Z","msg":"on lun 9"},{"pid":"b14f7a8418bd4156e8e246c257d96e7f38340a40","tid":2278510,"uid":28131,"like